query:
SELECT
    latitude,
    longitude,
    mmsi AS "mmsi!: Mmsi",
    TIMESTAMP AS msgtime,
    course_over_ground,
    navigation_status_id AS "navigational_status: NavigationStatus",
    rate_of_turn,
    speed_over_ground,
    true_heading,
    distance_to_shore
FROM
    ais_positions
WHERE
    mmsi = $1
    AND TIMESTAMP BETWEEN $2 AND $3
    AND $1 IN (
        SELECT
            mmsi
        FROM
            all_vessels
        WHERE
            mmsi = $1
            AND (
                ship_type IS NOT NULL
                AND NOT (ship_type = ANY ($4::INT[]))
                OR length > $5
            )
            AND (
                CASE
                    WHEN $6 = 0 THEN TRUE
                    WHEN $6 = 1 THEN length >= $7
                END
            )
    )
ORDER BY
    TIMESTAMP ASC
